Subject: Resignation Letter

Dear Sir,

I am writing to formally submit my resignation from my position as Senior Research Analyst at Koinet Media Pvt Ltd.

I have completed two years with the company, and I am deeply grateful for the opportunities and experiences gained during my tenure. However, to pursue further growth and career advancement, I have decided to explore new opportunities and take the next step in my professional journey.

I am committed to ensuring a smooth transition and will do my best to complete all pending tasks and assist with the handover process during my notice period. Please feel free to reach out if there is anything specific I can do to support the team.

Thank you for your guidance and support during my time here. I wish the company continued success in the future.

Sincerely,
Asmita Patil
